item.title: Dr. Bambang Purnomosidi D. P.
item.description: Dr. Bambang Purnomosidi D. P. (also known as bpdp) has a wide range of experiences in software industry and education. He is a Ph.D from DTETI (Departement Teknik Elektro dan Teknologi Informasi), Faculty of Engineering, Universitas Gadjah Mada.
